title: 163. Andy & DJ CTI: Lockdown At Disney, Pablo's Hippos & Slavery
itunes:title: 163. Andy & DJ CTI: Lockdown At Disney, Pablo's Hippos & Slavery
description: Are you a hippophobic? In today's Andy & DJ Cruise The Internet, they discuss the shutdown at the Shanghai Disney Land that resulted in 34,000 negative covid tests, the court ruling that identified Pablo Escobar's hippos as humans, and Colin Kaepernick comparing the NFL to slavery.
